Create grid/rows for sample, arms and timestamp in gB_Data just like the \original so we have values when test starts

Implement DAQ Log, Current Controller, Radian, and PAC Power

Users are not able to read inside gB_ChannelData checkboxes so they have no idea what they are selcting, I, as the developer just memorized what I select (A Jaw Line, B Jaw Line, C Jaw Line, etc...)